Name: Deep In the Heart Of Texas

!         G
1. The stars at night are big and bright
!                         D7
   deep in the heart of Texas
   the prairie sky is wide and high
!                         G
   deep in the heart of Texas.
2. The sage in bloom is like a perfume
   deep in the heart of Texas
   reminds me of the one I love
   deep in the heart of Texas.
3. The coyotes wail along the trail
   deep in the heart of Texas
   the rabbits tush around the brush
   deep in the heart of Texas.
4. The cowboys cry "ki-yip-pee-yi"
   deep in the heart of Texas
   the dogies bawl and bawl and bawl
   deep in the heart of Texas.
